<h1>YardS4le Centrum: About</h1>

<p>YardS4le Centrum is a site designed so that users may find yardsales near them.  Currently, most people advertise their yardsales by posting flyers on telephone poles or staking signs in the ground at major intersections.  This method of advertising is expensive, inefficient, and is typically bad for the community because people do not remove their signs after the sale is done.  On YardS4le Centrum you can digitally post your sale and add all the information you need people to know.  This includes the location, number of items, average value of the items, the hours of operation, and much much more.  Optionally, you may spend a small amount of money to make your sale "featured" where it will be posted right onto the home page.  Browse your local yardsale list or create your own posting today for free!  </p>
